dblp.social.updater
Class DblpUpdaterParser

java.lang.Object
  dblp.social.updater.DblpUpdaterParser

public class DblpUpdaterParser
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides a simple parser. This parser only recognizes some dblp tags needed to execute the stored queries. The stored queries are written knowing the result of the database mapping executed by Hibernate. If the mapping changes also the static strings defined in this class need to be changed.

Author:
staffiero
